Invocation Name: pitch pipe
des: On request, Alexa will play one of the following thirteen tones from a Tombo P13-E pitch pipe: A Natural, A Flat, B Natural, B Flat, C Natural, C Sharp, D Natural, E Flat, E Natural High, E Natural Low, F Natural, F Sharp, or G Natural.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
